  "content": "\n \n \n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"248\" data-backw=\"578\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"505092512\" data-ratio=\"0.4287037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f0d63b78-0303-47cc-c4e1-f4e72a111a00/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f0d63b78-0303-47cc-c4e1-f4e72a111a00/public\">\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section></h3>\n  <h3 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: -1.2em 8px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n        <p style=\"margin: -1.2em 8px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1em;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:inherit;\">新智元报道&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section></h3>\n  <section style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\">编辑：LRST</span>\n  </section>\n  <section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n     <h5 style=\"padding:10px;margin:10px 8px 0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;max-width:100%;word-break:break-all !important;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">【新智元导读】</strong>视觉+语音=更强的语音识别！BPO-AVASR通过优化音视频输入和输出偏好，提升语音识别在真实场景中的准确性，解决了传统方法在噪声、口语化和视觉信息利用不足的问题。<strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"></strong></span></h5>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-top: 24px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在日常生活中，你是否遇到过这样的情况：在嘈杂的环境中，语音助手听不清你的指令？或者在视频通话时，对方的发音不够清晰，让你难以理解？</span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">自动语音识别（ASR）技术正在不断进步，但在真实世界的视频场景中，ASR仍然面临许多挑战，如噪声干扰、口语化表达、以及同音词混淆等问题。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">那么，人们能否利用视觉信息来增强语音识别的准确性呢？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"320\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"352\" data-imgfileid=\"505092200\" data-ratio=\"0.568659127625202\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a82ed501-41f7-4b6a-3ef3-129f529eae00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"619\" data-width=\"619\" style=\"width: 57%;height: auto !important;flex-basis: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a82ed501-41f7-4b6a-3ef3-129f529eae00/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">最近，来自中国人民大学及卡耐基梅隆大学的学者们在AAAI 2025会议上正式发布了他们最新的研究——BPO-AVASR（Bifocal Preference Optimization for Audiovisual Speech Recognition）。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这是一种全新的双焦点偏好优化方法，能够有效提升多模态语音识别（AV-ASR）系统的性能，使其在真实世界视频场景下的表现更加强大！</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"131\" data-backw=\"578\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"505092757\" data-ratio=\"0.22685185185185186\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f661b3ec-a02e-4abc-83ba-ebfd28123b00/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f661b3ec-a02e-4abc-83ba-ebfd28123b00/public\"></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">论文链接：https://arxiv.org/pdf/2412.19005</span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">代码地址：https://github.com/espnet/espnet</span></p>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p>语音识别的「视觉外挂」：为什么要结合视觉？</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-top: 24px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">传统的ASR系统仅依赖音频输入进行语音识别，但在现实场景中，单靠音频往往不足以精准识别用户的语音。例如：</span>\n  </section>\n  <ul start=\"1\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">背景噪声问题：</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">咖啡厅、地铁、机场等嘈杂环境会干扰ASR的准确性。</span></span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">口语化表达：</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">自发性语音中包含大量连读、省略等非标准表达，例如「gonna」代替「going to」。</span></span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">同音词歧义：</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">例如，「dark」和「duck」，仅依赖音频可能会导致错误识别。</span></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\">视觉信息，尤其是视频中物体、背景信息、文</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">本等，能提供额外的线索来帮助ASR模型更精准地理解语音内容。例如，看到屏幕上出现了一瓶「可口可乐」，ASR 识别「cola」而非「caller」的可能性会更高。因此，AV-ASR（音视频语音识别）应运而生，结合视觉与语音信息，提升识别准确性。</span></p>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p>双焦点偏好优化（BPO）</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-top: 24px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">虽然多模态ASR近年来取得了显著进展，但目前的方法仍然存在一些关键问题：</span>\n  </section>\n  <ul start=\"1\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">未充分利用视觉信息：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">许多AV-ASR模型虽然引入了视觉特征，但并未明确优化模型在视觉线索上的利用能力。</span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">难以适应真实世界的视频场景：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">大多数方法仅在干净的数据集上训练，泛化能力有限。</span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">忽略真实环境中的常见错误：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">例如噪声影响、口语化表达、视觉信息缺失等问题。</span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了解决这些问题，研究者们提出了一种全新的双焦点偏好优化（Bifocal Preference Optimization, BPO）方法，以BPO-AVASR模型为核心。这篇工作的创新点包括：</span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">输入端偏好优化（Focal I）：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">通过遮挡音频或扰动视频信息，模拟现实世界中的干扰因素，使模型学会如何在音视频信息缺失时做出更准确的预测。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">输出端偏好优化（Focal II）：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">通过引入AI生成的错误文本（如同音词替换、语音模糊重写等），让模型学习如何避免这些常见的识别错误。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">换句话说，不仅要让模型学会「看」和「听」，更让它学会如何在信息不完整或错误的情况下做出更好的决策，从而更好地在多模态的场景下同时利用视觉和听觉信息识别出准确的文本。</span></p>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p>如何构造偏好数据？</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"407\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"519\" data-imgfileid=\"505092203\" data-ratio=\"0.7238493723849372\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ac64d80d-64b0-4508-c1f8-838d0870b200/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"717\" data-width=\"717\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ac64d80d-64b0-4508-c1f8-838d0870b200/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">BPO-AVASR架构概览</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 24px 8px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">BPO-AVASR通过构造偏好数据来优化ASR，主要涉及输入端优化和输出端优化。</span></p>\n  <section data-tool=\"markdown编辑器\" data-website=\"https://markdown.com.cn/editor\" style=\"padding:25px 30px;word-break:break-word;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:-10px;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:center;\">\n   <h1 data-tool=\"markdown.com.cn编辑器\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 24px;border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);display: inline-block;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">输入端偏好数据构造（Focal I）</span></strong></span></h1>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">目标：让模型学会如何处理不完整的音视频信息，提升对噪声、模糊信息的适应能力。</span></p>\n  <ul start=\"1\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">掩蔽音频（Masked Audio）：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">随机遮挡部分音频帧，模拟噪声环境。</span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">翻转视觉（Flipped Vision）：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对视频帧进行翻转，使视觉信息变得更难解析，以模拟视角变化的影响。</span>\n    </section></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section data-tool=\"markdown编辑器\" data-website=\"https://markdown.com.cn/editor\" style=\"padding:25px 30px;word-break:break-word;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-top:-10px;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:center;\">\n   <h1 data-tool=\"markdown.com.cn编辑器\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 24px;border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);display: inline-block;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;\">输出端偏好数据构造（Focal II）</span></h1>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">目标：让模型学习如何避免常见的识别错误，优化ASR预测文本的准确性。</span></p>\n  <ul start=\"1\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">同音词替换（Homophone-based Generation）：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">生成同音词错误，如「die」→「dye」。</span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">口语化改写（Spontaneous-based Generation）：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">生成口语化改写错误，如「gonna」→「goingto」。</span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">视觉信息忽略（Vision-based Generation）：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">让ChatGPT生成忽略视觉信息的错误文本，例如视频中的「dylon」被误识别为「dylan」。</span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"294\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"452\" data-imgfileid=\"505092199\" data-ratio=\"0.522543352601156\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c291b4ca-baee-49ad-b91d-164a0a94b700/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"865\" data-width=\"865\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c291b4ca-baee-49ad-b91d-164a0a94b700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">偏好数据构造方法</span></p>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p>实验结果与结论：BPO-AVASR让ASR更强大！</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-top: 24px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了验证BPO-AVASR的效果，研究者们在多个基准数据集上进行了测试，包括：How2，VisSpeech和Ego4D，在不同领域的多模态数据上验证了方法的有效性。</span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">实验结果表明，BPO-AVASR在大部分测试数据集上取得了SOTA（State-of-the-Art，最优）性能，尤其在嘈杂环境和复杂视频场景下表现出色。例如：</span></p>\n  <ul start=\"1\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在Ego4D数据集上，相比于现有的AV-ASR模型，BPO-AVASR的识别错误率（WER）降低了12.5%！</span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在How2数据集上，BPO-AVASR仅使用300小时的数据，就超越了使用131K小时数据训练的SOTA模型AVFormer！</span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"234\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"360\" data-imgfileid=\"505092197\" data-ratio=\"0.4161849710982659\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0b0a8dad-018a-498b-670a-1da85167cf00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"865\" data-width=\"865\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0b0a8dad-018a-498b-670a-1da85167cf00/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"352\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"542\" data-imgfileid=\"505092201\" data-ratio=\"0.6265895953757226\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f911df83-8bcf-4287-dff7-aeb5f55c4c00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"865\" data-width=\"865\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f911df83-8bcf-4287-dff7-aeb5f55c4c00/public\"></p>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p>未来展望：让 AI 更懂「看」与「听」</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-top: 24px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">BPO-AVASR的成功，不仅让ASR模型在复杂环境下更加稳定，同时也为未来的多模态学习提供了新的思路。未来，研究者们希望：</span>\n  </section>\n  <ul start=\"1\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">构建更大规模的开放域 AV-ASR 数据集，提升模型在各种场景下的泛化能力。</span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">探索更复杂的音视频理解，以多模态语音识别为基础，在更多的跨模态交互任务上提升复杂场景理解的能力。</span>\n    </section></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section style=\"white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\">参考资料：</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">https://arxiv.org/pdf/2412.19005</span></span></section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "人大和 CMU 提出的 BPO-AVASR 模型，通过双焦点偏好优化，显著提升了语音识别在复杂环境下的准确率，错误率降低 12.5%，为多模态语音识别研究提供了新思路。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "人大和 CMU 提出的 BPO-AVASR 模型，通过双焦点偏好优化，显著提升了语音识别在复杂环境下的准确率，错误率降低 12.5%，为多模态语音识别研究提供了新思路。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了中国人民大学和卡耐基梅隆大学联合提出的 BPO-AVASR 模型，该模型通过双焦点偏好优化方法，显著提升了多模态语音识别系统在真实世界视频场景下的性能。BPO-AVASR 的核心在于输入端偏好优化和输出端偏好优化：输入端模拟真实场景干扰，使模型适应不完整的音视频信息；输出端通过引入 AI 生成的错误文本，使模型避免常见的识别错误。实验结果表明，BPO-AVASR 在多个基准数据集上取得了 SOTA 性能，尤其在嘈杂环境和复杂视频场景下表现出色，在 Ego4D 数据集上，识别错误率降低了 12.5%。",
